## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="51816-138">下面的示例初始化<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder>类的新实例, 然后向其添加文本, 后跟音频文件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="51816-138">The following example initializes a new instance of the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder> class and then adds text to it, followed by an audio file.</span></span>  
  
